channel.title: Whats Good?
channel.description:
Super Mopar, sorry ive been gone past few months... I got grounded cause of my grades. Im proud to say im back..
Im here to ask, whats New? Anybody quit here? Any new RS updates? Any new things to talk about?
Tell me.. if anybody has any questions feel free to message me.

item.description:

Wait, why is Mscp shutting down?
[/quote]
